data.title: Roberto Palacios
data.meta_description: Roberto Carlos Palacios Mestas is a Peruvian former professional footballer who played as a midfielder.
data.text:
In this Spanish name, the first or paternalsurname is Palacios and the second or maternal family name is Mestas.

Roberto Carlos Palacios Mestas (born 28 December 1972) is a Peruvian former professional footballer who played as a midfielder.
